  "detailed_description": "<strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/5f07e1bc3202f51ad3c1bf8575a9c225.poster.avif?t=1680601993\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/5f07e1bc3202f51ad3c1bf8575a9c225.webm?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/5f07e1bc3202f51ad3c1bf8575a9c225.mp4?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Earn your stars in the single-player missions, unlocking all-new characters as you progress.<br></li><li>Try your hand at EIGHT different game modes; from the all new ‘Collect ‘Em Up’ to the more familiar ‘Deathmatch’ and ‘Last Man Standing’ modes.<br></li><li>Take the fight online and show the world who is the best.<br></li><li>Brace for the vivid colours and gameplay of the exciting locations - travel from the dusty Farm to the dominating City, the pirate bay to the war-torn outskirts and much more.<br></li><li>Featuring over 200 characters to unlock through play and purchase.<br></li><li>50 taunts to unleash your inner victory.<br></li><li>Upgrade your arsenal; with the Rifle, Shotgun and Rocket Launcher hidden in the world.<br></li><li>Fully featured tutorial to help learn the ropes.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/6e82930a4820488b7221ccec5d1a0c22.poster.avif?t=1680601993\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/6e82930a4820488b7221ccec5d1a0c22.webm?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/6e82930a4820488b7221ccec5d1a0c22.mp4?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/5f07e1bc3202f51ad3c1bf8575a9c225.poster.avif?t=1680601993\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/5f07e1bc3202f51ad3c1bf8575a9c225.webm?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/5f07e1bc3202f51ad3c1bf8575a9c225.mp4?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Earn your stars in the single-player missions, unlocking all-new characters as you progress.<br></li><li>Try your hand at EIGHT different game modes; from the all new ‘Collect ‘Em Up’ to the more familiar ‘Deathmatch’ and ‘Last Man Standing’ modes.<br></li><li>Take the fight online and show the world who is the best.<br></li><li>Brace for the vivid colours and gameplay of the exciting locations - travel from the dusty Farm to the dominating City, the pirate bay to the war-torn outskirts and much more.<br></li><li>Featuring over 200 characters to unlock through play and purchase.<br></li><li>50 taunts to unleash your inner victory.<br></li><li>Upgrade your arsenal; with the Rifle, Shotgun and Rocket Launcher hidden in the world.<br></li><li>Fully featured tutorial to help learn the ropes.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/6e82930a4820488b7221ccec5d1a0c22.poster.avif?t=1680601993\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/6e82930a4820488b7221ccec5d1a0c22.webm?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175250/extras/6e82930a4820488b7221ccec5d1a0c22.mp4?t=1680601993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
